== 逝世 ==
[[File:E7_10_000_TL_arka_yüz.jpg|thumb]]鈔票（1982年－1995年）的背面]]

希南於1588年逝世，葬在他設計的墓穴裡。他的墓地在塞利米耶清真寺北面的牆外，那邊的街道名為米馬爾·希南大道。他旁邊葬有蘇萊曼一世及其妻海賽克胡倫<ref>{{cite book | language = en | author = Icon Group International, Inc. | title = ''Tombs: Webster's Quotations, Facts and Phrases''  | year = 2008年  | publisher = Icon Group International, Inc. | isbn = 0546664253 | page = 第252頁 }}</ref>。

希南的名字又用於[[水星|水星]]的一個[[撞擊坑|撞擊坑]]，以及伊斯坦堡的[[米馬爾希南建築藝術大學|米馬爾希南建築藝術大學]]（Mimar Sinan University of Fine Arts）。

希南的肖像被印在1982年至1995年發行一萬元[[土耳其里拉|土耳其里拉]]鈔票的背面<ref>[http://www.tcmb.gov.tr/yeni/eng/ Central Bank of the Republic of Turkey]  {{webarchive|url=https://www.webcitation.org/5hFIaQq0J?url=http://www.tcmb.gov.tr/yeni/eng/ |date=2009-06-03 }}. Banknote Museum: 7. Emission Group - Ten Thousand Turkish Lira - [http://www.tcmb.gov.tr/yeni/banknote/E7/284.htm I. Series]  {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090729061754/http://www.tcmb.gov.tr/yeni/banknote/E7/284.htm |date=2009-07-29 }}, [http://www.tcmb.gov.tr/yeni/banknote/E7/286.htm II. Series]  {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090729061833/http://www.tcmb.gov.tr/yeni/banknote/E7/286.htm |date=2009-07-29 }}, [http://www.tcmb.gov.tr/yeni/banknote/E7/288.htm III. Series]  {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090729063212/http://www.tcmb.gov.tr/yeni/banknote/E7/288.htm |date=2009-07-29 }} & [http://www.tcmb.gov.tr/yeni/banknote/E7/290.htm IV. Series]  {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090729063638/http://www.tcmb.gov.tr/yeni/banknote/E7/290.htm |date=2009-07-29 }}. – Retrieved on 20 April 2009.</ref>。

